Usage<br/><br/>
grab (item)<br/><br/>
hold (item)<br/><br/>
<br/>
Lets you hold an item in the hand. This is used for wands and<br/>
staves. To use such an item you must hold<br/>
it in your hand. It is possible to hold an item in one hand, and wield a<br/>
singlehanded weapon in another.<br/>
